子或者用字<br />\n然後背起佢 考作文直接用<br />\n修辭靚 加扣到題冇離題 作文就好易高分<br />\n利申5*<br />\n加油 捱埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇小說代替有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果議論文係咪都係繼續背例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小說嘅話你要睇返作者文筆好唔好<br />\n同埋有冇靚修辭學 <br />\n因為有d流行小說可能重內容 <br />\n反而唔鍾意整色整水既修辭<br />\n但係真係要抄同記<br />\n落雨一個 好天又一個 寫景一個<br />\n 寫小朋友一個ect 總有個到時岩用<br />\n議論文我諗例子同結構條理個邊重要<br />\n但我當年都唔係作議論文 <br />\n希望有其他議論文叻嘅巴絲指教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66704152832196094648564c3b12c3d98870934b","tid":112380,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:30:57.000Z","msg":"文言文最易溫...<br />\n做哂個五本包你閱讀坐底有5<br />\n肯唔肯做睇你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年部份同學仔話閱讀唔洗溫 結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申4 core 5 Econ 5**"},{"pid":"b77032cb76cc5eed12b8049d7b1c634de637c372","tid":112380,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68990a74a44c8cd59da49d46c77e7abc1c67685b","tid":112380,"uid":15622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>文言文最易溫...<br />\n做哂個五本包你閱讀坐底有5<br />\n肯唔肯做睇你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年部份同學仔話閱讀唔洗溫 結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申4 core 5 Econ 5**</blockquote><br />\necon關咩事<br />\n係咪要讚你好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你隻hkcc傻鳩就收下嗲先啦"},{"pid":"cca67a6ecbf559a50f134513825107c19b85fdd9","tid":112380,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d85dcfcdf5d7ee769b68a9bfd83e013cf551af45","tid":112380,"uid":15622,